snippet.title: Johnny Depp in Court with Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Weighing in on the court battle between Johnny Depp and The Sun, with Amber Heard present to give testimony.  The two articles I read from are as follows:
The Guardian Article: "Johnny Depp Changed Story of Finger Injury, Court Hears."
https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jul/09/johnny-depp-praised-amber-heard-heroism-in-his-drugs-battle-court-hears

Mirror.com Article:
"Johnny Depp admits to 'accidentally' headbutting Amber Heard during heated row."
https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/johnny-depp-admits-accidentally-headbutting-22331560

Email me at jyenkotah@keeptruthalive.org
Follow me on Twitter @FantasyWeavers
Instagram: kateq9
